lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur will continue to use Wembley Stadium for their Europa League home ties if they qualify for the competition, manager Mauricio Pochettino said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Tottenham Will Stay at Wembley for Europa League-Pochettino
